text: aneka (yuda) pitivala (oba samkhyaven aduven tibiyadi) niyata vasayenma allah obata udav kara ætteya. ehet huneyin yuddha dinadi adhika satutata pat karamin tibu obage adhika (janagahanaye) samkhyava obata kisima prayojanayak at kara dunne næta. bhumiya metaram vistiranava tibiyadi (e atara eya) obata itamat hækili giyeya. tavada oba pitupasa harava duvannatada sidu viya
